For DBeaver Updates in SQL

Choose Components screen:
Select components to install -Checkmark only 2.  DBeaver Community and Include Java.  (leave the other 2 blank - Reset settings and Associate .SQL files)

Next

Choose Install Location:
C:\Users\User\AppData\Local\DBeaver

Next

Select Start Menu folder for shortcuts
DBeaver Community

Install

